message: "Miami-Dade State Attorney Katherine Fernandez Rundle said in a statement published by the NBC Miami website. “Restoring these lost girls to their families while getting their predatory bosses off the streets is what the Human Trafficking Task Force is really all about,”

data.description: Two teen girls have been rescued and two men have been arrested in South Florida in two separate human trafficking cases, according to local officials.
data.title: Two arrested, two teen girls rescued in Miami Beach human trafficking case - theGrio
